  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Also at 2nd level, you have learned to stay just out of eyesight, using minor distractions to shift attention away from yourself.</p><p> You can use your Genjutsu ability modifier in place of Dexterity when making a Stealth check.</p><p> By spending 1 Actualization Die, while you are hidden from a creature and use a feature or jutsu that would cause you break your stealth, you can choose to maintain your stealth, preventing creatures from learning your location.</p><p> Additionally, you have learned to make even the most obvious genjutsu subtle.</p><p> Choose a number of Genjutsu without the Unaware Keyword equal to half your proficiency bonus (rounded up) these jutsu gain Unaware keyword.</p><p></p>",
